snippet.title: Tales of the Drunken Paladin: Version 3
snippet.description:
The final and ultimate version of a classic RPG well over ten years in the making.

New content, improved mechanics, revised and rewritten dialogue... this is the RPG to play.

Learn more about me and what I do at https://www.patreon.com/stevegibbon.

It's out! Download it for free at www.drunkenpaladin.com

Music provided by bensound.com.
